{"tid":2363460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp 確定 2020 年加入廣告？網民怒：寧付 ＄8 都無咁嬲","createTime":"2021-01-12T08:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T12:41:30.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28434ee874f0e84919fe2ded8ee2430999f4cbc9","tid":2363460,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"香港人最常用的聊天軟件相信就是 WhatsApp 了。而大家喜歡它的原因很簡單，沒有廣告、免費使用（曾短暫推出收費系統）、跟手機號碼登記而且身邊很多人用。Whatsapp 早年被 Facebook 收購後，一直嘗試用不同方法開拓賺錢渠道。雖然不知不覺就拖了 5 年，但最終還是躲不過，近日有消息傳出 WhatsApp 即將在 2020 年正式加入廣告！<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報道，有參加 Facebook Marketing Summit 的網民曝光了幾張報告照片。從相中可見，WhatsApp 將會在 2020 年加入「Story Ads」類型的全屏廣告。幸好的是，這種廣告只會在用戶的狀態頁（Status）中出現，所以正常來説不會過分影響用戶的日常體驗。除了加入「Story Ads」，WhatsApp 都改善了不少商業用的功能，如訊息結構類型更豐富以及能夠直接跟 Facebook 的產品頁連動等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2355000/2357886/wap3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2355000%2F2357886%2Fwap3_600.jpg&h=ca6c7c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2355000/2357886/wap1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2355000%2F2357886%2Fwap1_600.jpg&h=2657e2d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民 Olivier_Ptv 分享 Facebook Marketing Summit 會上照片。<br />\n<br />\n面對 WhatsApp 最終決定要推出廣告，不少網民憤怒的留言，說：「功能又唔夠 wechat多，仲要加廣告，等收皮」、「係時候拉大隊轉telegram」、「講真情願佢收8$都無加廣告咁嬲 」、「X 唔 X 係嘛，呢啲通訊 app 都落廣告」、「有8蚊永久廣告移除即比錢」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，收網民都認為世上沒有免費午餐，認為免費 App 有廣告都算合理，指出：「其實 whatsapp 唔賣廣告係靠咩賺錢?」、「人地開發唔洗錢 maintenance唔洗成本，日日有班人係度做野 做地唔洗開飯既」。"},{"pid":"ed5edadeee146ef4091890d580528180281b28e8","tid":2363460,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"樓主係時空穿越者?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7471e78a35f422db279f612ba8928915e447696","tid":2363460,"uid":285328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:30:34.000Z","msg":"今日2021年1月12日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208e65d835c031b9ef591e96dd51a4255c9725fe","tid":2363460,"uid":69334,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:33:42.000Z","msg":"1蚊都唔會比，做唔住就自己消失啦，大把代替品<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721d5ee65fe5ba88472076014ef724bbc04fd398","tid":2363460,"uid":84783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:21:11.000Z","msg":"篇野吹奏we7<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841424dcc295eac11bae66e73cd575c91a408164","tid":2363460,"uid":113929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"We7 仲好，有國家免費 backup"}]}